::'''Watson:''' Hmph, the quickest way to stir up a pond of stagnant water is to throw in a nuclear bomb from the outside.
::'''Watson:''' Like... What's happening now.
::'''Watson:''' Oh, did you hear that? Don't mind me. I was just mumbling nonsense to myself.
