::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why don't you just throw a stone!?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010806-->
:::'''Watson:''' Hmph, young people!
:::'''Watson:''' A stone can cause a splash, but a nuclear bomb can trigger a tsunami!
:::'''Watson:''' Those who are smart will know how to take advantage of the tsunami and climb their way up the food chain.
:::{{A|VO vo ambient w0 greeting watson 101.ogg}} {{A|VO vo ambient w0 greeting watson 102.ogg}} '''Watson:''' I am Elizabeth Watson, the trendsetter of the new era.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do we know each other?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010811-->
:::'''Watson:''' ...Not really, but we can. I, Elizabeth Watson, can tell right away you are no ordinary person.
:::'''Watson:''' If you are like me and are unwilling to surrender to mediocrity, then we are siblings of a different mother.
:::'''Watson:''' This attack may seem like a disaster to many people, but it is an opportunity for those who are smart.
:::'''Watson:''' Seize it, my brethren. Nothing here is as simple as it seems.
::'''Watson:''' I heard how you destroyed the schemes of a Lord Ravager. It is rare for a youngster to have such outstanding talents, and you've earned this reward. I hope you retain the courage you showed at that moment throughout your life in the future.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
