:{{DIcon|undefined}} I heard that you've got a special assignment for me...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceD 800310101: Config/Level/Mission/8003101/Act/Act800310101.json-->
::----
::'''Watson:''' Oh? I didn't think the Lead Researcher's task force would be someone as young as you.
::'''Watson:''' But that's fine. An outsider like you has no way of interfering with my master plan...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you done speaking in riddles?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813100105-->
:::'''Watson:''' Based on your level of "understanding," perhaps my seniority and experience really does seem like a "riddle."
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So what's the special assignment?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813100107-->
:::'''Watson:''' Oh, young people these days. They just can't stay still and listen to a senior share their rich experience.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_813100108-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_813100108-->
::'''Watson:''' Forget it. Since you only care about those boring "assignments," let me explain.
::'''Watson:''' I'm sure even you know about efficiency here on the space station. Post-disaster recovery work is still going very slowly. And the guys in charge said it's because their access level is too low, and they don't have the appropriate authority.
::'''Watson:''' And what about those researchers with high-level access? They're either too old to help out in person, or they're working on something too huge to bother stooping down to this low level. So there's no way to provide any effective support.
::'''Watson:''' You know, those are just their excuses. At the end of the day, it's basically a supervisor wanting a "special agent" with the right permits to complete those special assignments, and they put in an application with the Lead Researcher for such a person &mdash; and that's why you are here.
::'''Watson:''' And rather unfortunately, I was asked to support this "Task Force" in getting things done as well as to handle all the paperwork.
::'''Watson:''' And based on this paperwork, I've got good news and bad news to tell ya.
::'''Watson:''' The good news: This assignment isn't hard at all. It's just a slight hassle at worst.
::'''Watson:''' And the bad news is... I've been tasked with some other urgent work. So this is about all the support I can offer you for now.
::'''Watson:''' I've sent the specific work details to you, so you can figure things out yourself later.
::----
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
